    "description": "《帕特里克的箱子无穷奇遇》是一款获奖的解谜游戏，可探索箱子套着箱子套着箱子套着箱子的独特循环系统。学会操控这个世界的结构，将箱子推到彼此内部以及再从内部推出。思考当箱子装下它自己时会出现什么情况，学会让无穷性为你所用。在不断深入系统的过程中，探索更多的机制和循环曲折。一路都是无数箱子带来的精彩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/467a398368c2ef43cc607472cbecdbaf.poster.avif?t=1745611653\" width=356 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/467a398368c2ef43cc607472cbecdbaf.webm?t=1745611653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/467a398368c2ef43cc607472cbecdbaf.mp4?t=1745611653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这款游戏含有 350 多个人工打造的谜题，不仅会让你陷入思考，也会为你引导并展现整个系统的美妙之处。每个谜题都含有新的创意；山重水复疑无路，柳暗花明又一村。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/d25e78d14aeb82b7344d24467e052eee.poster.avif?t=1745611653\" width=356 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/d25e78d14aeb82b7344d24467e052eee.webm?t=1745611653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260520/extras/d25e78d14aeb82b7344d24467e052eee.mp4?t=1745611653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>令人心旷神怡、充满好奇气息的原声和声音由 Priscilla Snow 打造，在新的机制出现时烘托氛围。<br><br>《帕特里克的箱子无穷奇遇》曾在 2020 年独立游戏节 (Independent Games Festival 2020) 上获得设计卓越奖 (Excellence in Design)。这款游戏还曾入选 2019 年 IndieCade 独立游戏展会，并获得 IndieCade 开发者选择奖 (IndieCade Developers Choice)。",
